title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4606.11 - Interest in another games of chance premises prohibited
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4606.11 - Interest in another games of chance premises prohibited

State Regulations

No organization shall be eligible to receive or be issued
a license as a games of chance lessor if such organization shall have any
interest, direct or indirect, in other premises for which an authorized games
of chance lessor's license has been issued. Notes
